<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>An instance of <db:link xlink:href="qmediaobject.xml">QMediaObject</db:link> (or its derived classes) can report any changes in availability via this control.</db:para>
<db:para>The interface name of <db:link xlink:href="qmediaavailabilitycontrol.xml">QMediaAvailabilityControl</db:link> is <db:code>org.qt-project.qt.mediaavailabilitycontrol/5.0</db:code> as defined in <db:link xlink:href="qmediaavailabilitycontrol.xml#QMediaAvailabilityControl_iid">QMediaAvailabilityControl_iid</db:link>.</db:para>
